RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT DISTINCT RATE_CODE, DESCRIPTION FROM CFTM_FLOATING_RATE_CODE WHERE /*BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND*/ RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' UNION SELECT DISTINCT A.RATE_CODE,A.RATE_DESCR FROM CFTMS_RFR_MASTER A WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND TYPE = NVL(?,TYPE)
SELECT RATE_CODE,RATE_CODE_DESC FROM LFTMS_STANDARD_RATE_CODE WHERE RATE_TYPE='P' AND RECORD_STAT='O' AND AUTH_STAT='A'

SELECT DISTINCT FIELD_NAME AS RATE_CODE, FIELD_DESC AS RATE_DESCR FROM OLTMS_STATIC_MAINTENANCE WHERE MAINTENANCE_TYPE = 'RTCD' AND FIELD_TYPE = 'A' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' ORDER BY RATE_CODE
SELECT RULE_ID, DESCRIPTION FROM LFTB_ICCF_RLAVL WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND RULE_TYPE = 'I'

SELECT CCY_CODE, CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' /*AND CCY_CODE NOT IN (SELECT CURRENCY FROM LFTMS_PRODUCT_CURRENCY_LIMITS WHERE PRODUCT = :BLK_CSTM_PRODUCT.PRODUCT_CODE AND COMPONENT = :BLK_LFTMS_INTEREST_CLASS.ORIGINAL_COMPONENT)*/
SELECT CLASS_CODE FROM LFTMS_INTEREST_CLASS WHERE MODULE = ?
SELECT CLASS_CODE, CLASS_DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_CLASS WHERE MODULE = ? AND CLASS_TYPE = 'IN' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' ORDER BY CLASS_CODE

SELECT DISTINCT A.RATE_CODE, B.FIELD_DESC FROM LFTMS_TREASURY_RATE_CODE A, OLTMS_STATIC_MAINTENANCE B WHERE A.RATE_CODE = B.FIELD_NAME AND A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND A.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND B.MAINTENANCE_TYPE = 'RTCD' AND B.FIELD_TYPE = A.RATE_CODE_USAGE AND ? = 'T' UNION SELECT RATE_CODE, RATE_CODE_DESC FROM (SELECT DISTINCT A.RATE_CODE AS RATE_CODE, A.DESCRIPTION AS RATE_CODE_DESC FROM CFTM_FLOATING_RATE_CODE A/*, CFTMS_FLOAT_RATE_MASTER B*/ WHERE /*A.RATE_CODE = B.RATE_CODE AND*/ A.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' /*AND A.BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND A.BRANCH_CODE = B.BRANCH_CODE*/ AND (? = 'U' AND 'D' = (SELECT PRODUCT_TYPE FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_MASTER_LD WHERE PRODUCT = ?)) UNION SELECT RATE_CODE, RATE_CODE_DESC FROM LFTMS_STANDARD_RATE_CODE WHERE RATE_TYPE = 'S' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND (? <> 'U' OR 'D' <> (SELECT PRODUCT_TYPE FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT_MASTER_LD WHERE PRODUCT = ?))) WHERE ? <> 'T'
